column5: Can anyone give me any fishing info for Prairie Bee Lake? Or any of the portage lakes? Heading there June 20-27 for first time and the owner don't have much experience fishing the lake. We'll be staying the main camp not the outpost. Thanks, Jim

Several reports if you do a search. Very good reputation for smallmouth, numbers but not size on walleye. I've stayed at Windermere and the hosts had good information. I'm sure they'll have some reports as the season progresses.
